                <note rend="inline" type="source">882.5048/241: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the Chargé in Liberia</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Carter</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1930-02-19T18:00:00-05:00"
                            >February 19, 1930—6 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>21. As Christy cannot complete his arrangements this week, he has had to postpone
                    his sailing until March 7, arriving Monrovia March 20.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Cotton</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
